data.chText: （计算机荧光屏上的）光标，游标
data.enText: a small mark on a computer screen that can be moved and that shows the position on the screen where, for example, text will be added

means: (计算机荧光屏上的)光标，游标

tr: (computer science) indicator consisting of a movable spot of light (an icon) on a visual display
moving it allows the user to point to commands or screen positions

value.def: On a computer screen, the cursor is a small shape that indicates where anything that is typed by the user will appear.
